scribe the general nature and level of work being performed by people assigned to this job they are not intended to be an exhaustive list of all responsibilities duties and skills required of personnel working within this job title convergys is an eeoaamfvetdisability employer discover your career your first position at convergys is just the beginning of something incredible the first step in a path towards a lasting career customer service careers make a difference every day by providing superior customer service learn more military family opportunities you served our nation with honor now it is our turn to honor your commitment as one of our own learn more about convergys as a military friendly employer learn more healthcare agent careers our healthcare licensing program help fits your lifestyle and you can take it wherever you go find out how you can become a healthcare agent learn more career search  apply  convergys home about corporate leadership global  supplier diversity industry recognition locations mission  values social responsibility careers change location search  apply client solutions industries we serve automotive communications  media financial services healthcare insurance retail technology travel  hospitality utilities capabilities we offer outsourcing services customer care revenue generation technical support collections home agent chat agent customer experience analytics analytics voice of the customer integrated cx insights technologies omnichannel  selfservice robotic process automation network solutions challenges we solve customer experience sales effectiveness customer retention cost management compliance  fraud protection delivery options global multilingual hubs resources articles brochures case studies client testimonials data sheets events infographics newsletters research video webinars whitepapers investors releases events  presentations releases events  presentations key financial information sec filings gaap reconciliations financ