usiness convergys acquired intervoice a dallasbased telecommunications company in  for  million convergys sold its human resources management line of business to northgatearinso in march  on march   japanese technology firm nec announced it would buy the information management business of convergys for approximately  million in  convergys philippines  years after its entry into the country established  centers with  employees in all was named “bpo employer of the year” at the annual international ict awards on april   convergys completed the acquisition of new zealandbased datacom call center operations in kuala lumpur and manila for  million on january   convergys and stream global services announced entry into a definitive merger under the agreement convergys would acquire stream for a total enterprise value of  million in cash on march   convergys completed the acquisition of stream creating the nd largest bpo provider in the outsourcing industry the merger brought their total employees to approximately  with  centers in  countries supporting  languages see alsoedit list of companies in the united states list of sp  companies referencesedit  a b c d e f g  annual report pdf convergys feb   retrieved may     fontenay blake apr   cbis matrixx team to form new company orlando sentinel retrieved may     ipo daily report citysearch to merge with ticketmaster online marketwatch aug   retrieved may     cincinnati company will buy digitalthink for m san francisco business times mar   retrieved may     convergys to acquire intervoice for  million the new york times jul   retrieved may     hausmann daniel mar   kkrbacked deal offers alternative to scrantonstyle hr the wall street journal retrieved may     alabaster jay mar   nec to acquire convergys data management business for us million cio retrieved may     convergys named bpo employer of the year abscbn news apr   retrieved may     talevski julia apr   datacom sells asia bpo assets for  million arn retrieved may     ch