ncome   million  total assets   billion  total equity   billion  number of employees   website wwwconvergyscom convergys corporation is a corporation based in cincinnati ohio that sells customer management and information management products primarily to large corporations customer management products include agent assisted selfservice and care software tailored to the communications financial services technology retail healthcare and government markets information management provides convergent billing and business support system bss products and services including revenue management product and order management and customer care management to telecom utilities and cablesatellitebroadband service providers they have approximately  employees across  countries contents  history  see also  references  external links historyedit one of the convergys offices in gurgaon india the company grew from cincinnati bell information systems and matrixx both subsidiaries of cincinnati bell and att solutions customer care formerly att american transtech which was sold to cincinnati bell in  an ipo in august  made it a fully independent company since then convergys headquarters in cincinnati ohio has acquired numerous companies in  convergys bought digitalthink for  million digitalthink helped convergys expand its human resources outsourcing business convergys acquired intervoice a dallasbased telecommunications company in  for  million convergys sold its human resources management line of business to northgatearinso in march  on march   japanese technology firm nec announced it would buy the information management business of convergys for approximately  million in  convergys philippines  years after its entry into the country established  centers with  employees in all was named “bpo employer of the year” at the annual international ict awards on april   convergys completed the acquisition of new zealandbased datacom call center operations in kuala lumpur and manila for  million 